N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 206.21 - Judicial Review

State Regulations
A decision by the Commission, to deny, suspend, or revoke an
application, license or certificate issued or to otherwise discipline a
licensee, permit holder, or other authorized person or entity pursuant to this

Part shall be reviewable pursuant to Article 78 of the New York Civil Practice
and Rules Law. Notes
